    "If a number is going to be changed, a number within the possible range for that parameter is generated.",
    "Accordingly, the new generated chromosome would be valid.• Crossover: For the crossover, two parents are selected.",
    "Each parent is chosen by tournament selection.",
    "Based on a predetermined probability, a crossover may occur, or the parents are directly copied to the children population.",
    "This strategy ensures the preservation of superior-quality solutions.If crossover happens, each of the 15 numbers can be swapped between two parents with a probability of 50 percent."
